    <description>Tutanota is the world's most secure email service, easy to use and private by design. Sign up for free encrypted email now.

With end-to-end encryption and 2FA, your emails have never been more secure. The built-in encryption guarantees that your mailbox belongs to you: Nobody can decrypt or read your data.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Tutanota is an email client with a strong focus on security and privacy that lets you encrypt emails on all your devices.</summary>
    <releaseNotes># What's new
 - Update libs [#10540](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10540)
 - Change plans with Drive support [#10537](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10537)
 - Fix DriveMoveItemDialog height [#10534](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10534)
 - Fix font icon sizes [#10532](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10532)
 - drive: improved mime type processing and colorful file icons [#10529](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10529)
 - [build] Update undici to 7.24.4 [#10517](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10517)
 - use new icon naming conventions [#10513](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10513)
 - Various Drive-related improvements [#10448](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10448)
 - Improve blob decryption speed in browser [#10434](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10434)
 - Drive: drag-and-drop improvements [#10433](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10433)
 - Drive: deselect items by clicking on empty space [#10319](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10319)
 - More sensible context menu and action bar entries [#10315](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10315)
 - Drive: Show UserError for copy/move item to Trash [#10307](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10307)

# Bugfixes
 - Older repeating events do not show up in calendar widget [#10427](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10427)
 - Overflowing repeating event doensnt show up on the next [#10241](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10241)

